-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                     CRAMP
                       Cramp Runs And Monitors Processes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        CRAMP is an engine to run complex test cases in user specified order.
The CRAMP framework provides a function profiler library, a memory monitoring
feature, function call graph generator and grab other process status. CRAMP
can be used on Microsoft Windows 2000+ as it uses lot of Win32 APIs. This
could be considered as a major drawback.

Some features:
UI:
        1. Provide a UI for generating the scenario file in XML format
        2. The same UI to analyse/edit an existing scenario file
        3. Launch CRAMP engine from UI
